      <title>资源网站</title>
      <link href="/2023/02/07/%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99/"/>
      <url>/2023/02/07/%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h1 id="资源网站"><a href="#资源网站" class="headerlink" title="资源网站"></a>资源网站</h1><p><strong>只因知道了这15个神级网站，就能白嫖全世界资源!照片&#x2F;壁纸&#x2F;AI语音&#x2F;音频视频素材&#x2F;图标&#x2F;插画&#x2F;字体&#x2F;电子书&#x2F;画作&#x2F;地图</strong></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071614001.jpeg" alt="img"></p><p><strong>一、照片</strong></p><p>1、Unsplash：<a href="https://unsplash.com/">https://unsplash.com/</a></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071614694.jpeg" alt="img"></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071603263.jpeg" alt="img"></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071614461.jpeg" alt="img"></p><p>只支持英文进行搜索</p><p>2、pixabay：<a href="https://pixabay.com/zh/">https://pixabay.com/zh/</a></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071615377.jpeg" alt="img"></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071615594.jpeg" alt="img"></p><p><strong>二、壁纸</strong></p><p>0、Wallpaper Engine</p><p>在steam商城下载（收费）</p><p>1、wallhaven：<a href="https://wallhaven.cc/">https://wallhaven.cc/</a></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071615642.jpeg" alt="img"></p><p>2、极简壁纸：<a href="https://bz.zzzmh.cn/">https://bz.zzzmh.cn/</a></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556732.jpeg" alt="img"></p><p>国内的网站，全部的资源来源于上一个网站，访问速度更快，界面简洁。</p><p><strong>三、AI语音</strong></p><p>1、微软Azure项目：<a href="https://azure.microsoft.com/zh-cn/products/cognitive-services/text-to-speech/#overview">https://azure.microsoft.com/zh-cn/products/cognitive-services/text-to-speech/#overview</a></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556768.jpeg" alt="img"></p><p><strong>四、音频&#x2F;视频素材</strong></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556688.jpeg" alt="img"></p><p>1、哔哩哔哩：<a href="https://www.bilibili.com/">https://www.bilibili.com/</a></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071603031.jpeg" alt="img"></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556532.jpeg" alt="img"></p><p><strong>五、图标&#x2F;插画</strong></p><p>1、iconfont：<a href="https://www.iconfont.cn/">https://www.iconfont.cn/</a></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556159.jpeg" alt="img"></p><p><strong>六、字体</strong></p><p>1、100font：<a href="https://www.100font.com/">https://www.100font.com/</a></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556727.jpeg" alt="img"></p><p>2、fontspace：<a href="https://www.fontspace.com/">https://www.fontspace.com/</a></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556960.jpeg" alt="img"></p><p><strong>七、电子书</strong></p><p>1、鸠摩搜索：<a href="https://www.jiumodiary.com/">https://www.jiumodiary.com/</a></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556950.jpeg" alt="img"></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556029.jpeg" alt="img"></p><p>2、古腾堡计划：<a href="https://gutenberg.org/">https://gutenberg.org/</a></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556672.jpeg" alt="img"></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556703.jpeg" alt="img"></p><p><strong>八、画作</strong></p><p>1、麦田艺术：<a href="https://www.nbfox.com/">https://www.nbfox.com/</a></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556760.jpeg" alt="img"></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556727.jpeg" alt="img"></p><p>2、芝加哥艺术博物馆The Collection 项目：<a href="https://www.artic.edu/collection?is_public_domain=1">https://www.artic.edu/collection?is_public_domain=1</a></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556249.jpeg" alt="img"></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556307.jpeg" alt="img"></p><p><strong>九、地图</strong></p><p>1、标准地图服务系统：<a href="http://bzdt.ch.mnr.gov.cn/">http://bzdt.ch.mnr.gov.cn/</a></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556392.jpeg" alt="img"></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556344.jpeg" alt="img"></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556708.jpeg" alt="img"></p><p>2、大卫拉姆齐地图图书馆：<a href="https://www.davidrumsey.com/">https://www.davidrumsey.com/</a></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556871.jpeg" alt="img"></p><p><img src="https://zhihua-blog.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ima/202302071556892.jpeg" alt="img"></p><p>本篇文章资源搜集自：【只因知道了这15个神级网站，就能白嫖全世界资源！照片&#x2F;壁纸&#x2F;AI语音&#x2F;音频视频素材&#x2F;图标&#x2F;插画&#x2F;字体&#x2F;电子书&#x2F;画作&#x2F;地图】 <a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1nR4y1h7WM/?share_source=copy_web&vd_source=07c3b22be3b5545d0a2e606a6053307d">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1nR4y1h7WM/?share_source=copy_web&amp;vd_source=07c3b22be3b5545d0a2e606a6053307d</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
